name: Ancient Tablets of King Femi: Rose Quartz
description:
Delicately rolled beneath a waterfall somewhere in the outermost West of the world.
She sings.
She beautifully rejoices.
All who walk above her feel her essence yet do not feel entrapped.
The sensation of her knowledge is loving and intimate.
Sweet, kind and pure.
She tells the secrets of heart matters.
Speaks poetry to the Soul.
Graceful and elegant.
Her mantra is an angels chant.
